{
  "title": "Motion Design",
  "html": "<main><header class=\"section-page-header\"><div class=\"row d-flex justify-content-between\"><div class=\"col col-sm-10\"></div><!----></div><!----><h1>Motion Design</h1><p class=\"text-secondary mb-0\"> How to create graphics and animations for broadcast using Motion Design. </p><!----></header><!----><div class=\"row\"><div class=\"col-lg-9 print-w-100\"><div class=\"b-img\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" class=\"img-fluid\" alt=\"Motion Design\" width=\"1920\" height=\"335\" loading=\"lazy\" fetchpriority=\"auto\" decoding=\"auto\" ng-img=\"true\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/e8f89465-80cc-47c2-afd9-62aad0761244?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335\" srcset=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/e8f89465-80cc-47c2-afd9-62aad0761244?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=1920&amp;height=335 1x, https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/e8f89465-80cc-47c2-afd9-62aad0761244?resizing_type=fill&amp;width=3840&amp;height=670 2x\"></div><!----><!----><!----><header class=\"document-header mb-3 d-lg-none d-print-none\"><content-nav class=\"content-nav is-collapsible\" ngh=\"6\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></content-nav></header><!----><article><!----><!----><div document-content-blocks-renderer=\"\" class=\"d-block\" ngh=\"12\"><div id=\"content-blocks-renderer\" class=\"content-blocks-renderer\"><block-switch-control class=\"block-switch-control\" ngh=\"7\"><!----></block-switch-control><block-switch-info class=\"block-switch-info\" ngh=\"8\"><!----></block-switch-info><blocks-renderer id=\"blocks-renderer\" ngh=\"11\"><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Motion Design is a feature set for motion graphics artists who need a streamlined and creative suite of tools that provide for rapid iteration and scalability. Motion Design includes a reworked world outliner, user interface, rigging tools, cloners, customizable 2D/3D shapes, and a new way to create materials using a streamlined, layer-based workflow called Material Designer.</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">Everything you create can be rigged with customizable logic that you can version using a variety of approachable solutions. Motion Design offers a robust Rundown tool that, in conjunction with its Transition Logic system, can run live-updated broadcast graphics with minimal rigging.</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><p internal-link-handler=\"\">All of Motion Design's features combine to help you create on-air compatible graphics as well as high-end 3D product design and advertising visuals.</p><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><h2 id=\"using-motion-design\" data-previous-ids=\"usingmotiondesign\"> Using Motion Design </h2><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><ul block-document-list=\"\" class=\"block-document-list\" ngh=\"10\"><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:motion-design-quickstart-guide-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/9b007517-ccf0-4409-a021-864fedadca39?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Motion Design Quick Start Guide\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Motion Design Quick Start Guide</p><p class=\"description\">Get started working with Motion Design.</p></div></div></a></li><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:your-first-graphic-with-motion-design-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/9c67fcd2-56c6-46fb-8d42-f0424b6918a7?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Your First Graphic with Motion Design\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Your First Graphic with Motion Design</p><p class=\"description\">Learn how to create your first graphic using Motion Design.</p></div></div></a></li><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:motion-design-cloners-and-effectors-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/8c03d613-bada-4a3d-897e-347e0330963b?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Cloners and Effectors\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Cloners and Effectors</p><p class=\"description\">An overview for using Cloners and Effectors in Motion Design.</p></div></div></a></li><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:setting-up-rundown-server-for-motion-design-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/84ee1447-6e6e-4f32-8e8a-0d8e93c16499?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Rundown Server\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Rundown Server</p><p class=\"description\">See how the Rundown Server loads the rundown assets and page templates for Motion Design.</p></div></div></a></li><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:operator-stack-in-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/f0a20f0c-ff06-49b0-8853-d2173c0508d2?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Operator Stack\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Operator Stack</p><p class=\"description\">Use the Operator Stack window to access Modifiers and Animators for your Motion Design project.</p></div></div></a></li><li block-dir-item=\"\" ngh=\"9\"><a internal-link-handler=\"\" class=\"document-list-card\" href=\"#unreal-doc:scene-state-for-unreal-engine\"><div class=\"thumbnail-container\"><img class=\"unreal-doc-img\" loading=\"lazy\" width=\"120\" height=\"92\" class=\"thumbnail\" src=\"https://dev.epicgames.com/community/api/documentation/image/cd04fa21-6d01-4885-9505-32f95ea190cd?resizing_type=fit&amp;width=640&amp;height=640\" alt=\"Scene State\"></div><div class=\"document-list-card-content\"><!----><div class=\"document-list-card-content-info\"><p class=\"title\">Scene State</p><p class=\"description\">An overview of Motion Design Scene State.</p></div></div></a></li><!----></ul><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----><!----></blocks-renderer></div><!----></div></article><tags-list class=\"mt-1 d-print-no